## **1. Matrices & Determinants**
### **Key Concepts:**
- Types of matrices (symmetric, skew-symmetric, orthogonal, etc.)
- Matrix operations (addition, multiplication, transpose, inverse)
- Properties of determinants
- Rank of a matrix
- Cramerâ€™s rule

