## **3. Eigenvalues & Eigenvectors**
### **Key Concepts:**
- Definition & properties
- Characteristic equation
- Diagonalization of matrices
- Cayley-Hamilton theorem
- Applications in stability analysis & vibrations

### **Study Resources:**
- **Video Lectures:**  
  - [3Blue1Brown - Eigenvectors Explained Visually](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PFDu9oVAE-g)  
  - [NPTEL - Eigenvalues & Eigenvectors (IIT Madras)](https://nptel.ac.in/courses/111/105/111105078/)  

- **Textbooks:**  
  - *Linear Algebra Done Right* â€“ Sheldon Axler  
  - *Engineering Mathematics* â€“ GATE Academy Publications  

- **Practice Problems:**  
  - [GATE Previous Year Questions](https://gateoverflow.in/questions/tagged/eigenvalues)  
  - [Problems from Schaumâ€™s Outline of Linear Algebra](https://www.mheducation.com/)  

